      "message": "Per our discussion in chat, I changed to use a single channel (per data type) with a goroutine which feeds modified data onto internal channels for each modified client.  Each modified client has an associated goroutine which reads from the internal channel and writes to the returned channel, closing the returned channel when the context expires.",
